<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="resist-v">resist <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'zɪst/    美 /rɪ'zɪst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-oppose">1.★ <strong>抗拒 (oppose)：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>resist doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The bank strongly resisted cutting interest rates. 
银行强烈反对降息。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[常用于否定句] 忍住；抵制：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I can’t <strong>resist the temptation</strong>. 
我抵制不了这种诱惑。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I finished the cake. <strong>I couldn’t resist it</strong>. 
我忍不住把蛋糕吃光了。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>resist doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He found it <strong>hard to resist buying</strong> these books. 
他发现忍住不买这些书很难。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>抵抗：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>resist an enemy attack 
抵抗敌人的进攻</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>resistance /rɪ'zɪstəns/ n   </p></div>